Ask HN: Working on Any Radio, SWL, FM/MW/TV DX, or Amateur Radio Projects?
text: Just curious what anybody else is up to in radio. I'm making some basic plans to get into SOTA locally. Listening to some Radio NZ in the 15 MHz band here in California in the hammock during the evening. Hopping on local repeaters or simplex when I can. And playing with favorite AM/MW receivers.
